/* MainDOB DobPicture — Bitmap Paint Program
 *
 * Architecture:
 *   Canvas: uint32_t pixel buffer (BGR format, 0x00BBGGRR)
 *           Up to 4096x4096. Allocated via malloc.
 *   Viewport: scrollable/zoomable view into the canvas.
 *   Palette: 18 fixed colors + 6 user-defined slots.
 *   RGB mixer: 3 sliders (0-255) + textboxes + live preview.
 *   Tools: pencil, eraser, rectangle, circle, with size control.
 *   Export: BMP 24-bit (extensible to JPG/PNG).
 *   File I/O: via DobFileSystem Entry Point stubs.
 *
 * Panel commands: Nuovo, Apri, Salva, Esporta BMP
 *
 * Future (V2): fountain pen, airbrush, selection/copy,
 *              fill tool, undo, JPG/PNG, Entry Point API.
 */

